Don't Marry Proboards Forum Archive.zip

This is a forum archive of the original Don't Marry Forum.
Originally located at http://dontmarry.proboards27.com/ and www.dontmarry.com.

For anyone unfamiliar with the history of the site, the message boards were bombarded by trolls and spammed with pornography until someone complained and the forum was shut down. The site owner moved traffic to a forum on the site itself, and the level of traffic almost immediately exceeded the bandwidth allocation, effectively shutting the site down.

60 MB zip file that extracts to a series of pdf archives.
